Interface IAction

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Controller, ExternalProgramRunner, IGraphSchedule, ISchedulableAction, ISchedule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAction, AbstractDataSetManager.ScheduledDataSet, CallBackAction, ContextFreezeDryingAction, DefaultAction, DefaultController, DefaultExtProgRunner, DefaultGraphSchedule, DynamicTargetAction, ExternalModelRunner, IterableCallBackAction, PhysicsScheduleAction, Schedule, ScheduleGroup, StateChartBeginAction, StateChartResolveAction, StopEnabledCallBackAction, ThreadedAction

    public interface IAction
    Interface for executable object. Schedules execute objects that implement this type either directly or by creating an IAction to perform the appropriate execution.
